queries.query: INSERT INTO `users` (`vFirstName`, `vLastName`, `vUserName`, `vEmail`, `vMobileNo`, `dDob`, `vPassword`, `tAddress`, `vCity`, `dLatitude`, `dLongitude`, `iStateId`, `vStateName`, `vZipCode`, `eStatus`, `dtAddedAt`, `eDeviceType`, `vDeviceModel`, `vDeviceOS`, `vDeviceToken`, `app_section`, `vProfession`, `eEmailVerified`, `vEmailVerificationCode`, `vTermsConditionsVersion`, `vPrivacyPolicyVersion`) VALUES ('Ravi', 'Sherton', 'ravi007', 'ravi.sherton@gmail.com', '7833434322', '', '$2y$10$Vv9lajBUrUXqG0ugsFmc0eL2m3D4rKq9PPjMilpRrp8X2mCJSduQ6', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Inactive', NOW(), 'android', 'moto e4 plus', 'android', 'cphA3nDBIHo:APA91bFXD2XZDMD0uAdyWZWne_eT-I97HO0jGdwOv-px7WD6kzG6fTygF5cbTS11jfJ5dsK5KymvrQuRdgFtJFuGWADdx5yPcUOQwOXqG_taKuCe-lkSZNQZm0HQK5Yffads_KcWsobC', 'Dating', 'Doctor', 'No', 'cmF2aS5zaGVydG9uQGdtYWlsLmNvbSYxNjA1NzgxNTMx', '1.0', '1.0')

SELECT `u`.`iUserId` AS `u_user_id`,`u`.`vFirstName` AS `u_first_name`,`u`.`vLastName` AS `u_last_name`,`u`.`vUserName` AS `u_user_name`,`u`.`vEmail` AS `u_email`,`u`.`vMobileNo` AS `u_mobile_no`,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `u_profile_image`,`u`.`dDob` AS `u_dob`,`u`.`tAddress` AS `u_address`,`u`.`vCity` AS `u_city`,`u`.`dLatitude` AS `u_latitude`,`u`.`dLongitude` AS `u_longitude`,`u`.`iStateId` AS `u_state_id`,`u`.`vStateName` AS `u_state_name`,`u`.`vZipCode` AS `u_zip_code`,`u`.`eStatus` AS `u_status`,(concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName)) AS email_user_name,`u`.`eLogStatus` AS `u_log_status_updated` FROM `users` AS `u` WHERE `u`.`iUserId` = 221  LIMIT 1
